use MAVEN for building project

ScalaFX project don't have maven artifact today. To use it, you must add scalafx_2.10-1.0.0-M1.jar file manually to yours local repository, see:

http://code.google.com/p/scalafx/downloads/list

mvn install:install-file -DartifactId=scalafx -DgroupId=org.scalafx -Dpackaging=jar -Dfile=scalafx_2.10-1.0.0-M1.jar -Dversion=2.10-1.0.0-M1